item.title: No title
item.description: Come on out to join my band and I as we introduce new music for my first full-length studio album. You will be my ears for the evening as I try out the new material and let you be the judge and jury. I know that's a lot to throw at you but I figure we've been friends for so long and you've supported me and the music all along so who better to share in this experience and give me your feedback. I value that more than you'll ever know.
